then let the whole of <LOCATION> Lebanon </LOCATION> and the whole of the <LOCATION> Middle </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Eest </LOCATION> go up in flames,'' he said. The pope has expressed outrage at the recent fighting in <LOCATION> Lebanon </LOCATION> and last week said he felt an `` imperative'' to visit the country.
